<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٣٠- عَبد اللهِ بْن ذَكوان.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ عَبد الصَّمد:</span> حدَّثنا عَبد اللهِ، حدَّثنا مُحَمد بْن المُنكَدِر.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>مُنكَرُ الحديثِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فِي الأذان.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>